commit.message:
fix: Remove Coordinate constructor validation to allow boundary testing

- Remove immediate bounds validation from Coordinate constructor
- Add isValid() method for coordinate validation
- Move validation responsibility to Board.placeShip() method
- This allows testing boundary conditions as required by acceptance criteria
